    <item>
      <title>日本央行通过区域报告暗示其仍将加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/boj-signals-it-remains-on-rate-hike-path-with-regional-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行上调了对两个地区经济体的评估，暗示其仍将考虑进一步加息，但同时也没有证据表明需要立即采取行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/boj-signals-it-remains-on-rate-hike-path-with-regional-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:43:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈利法克斯称英国房价连续第三个月上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/uk-house-prices-climb-for-a-third-month-halifax-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈利法克斯的数据显示，由于抵押贷款利率降低和收入增加刺激更多买家进入市场，英国房价 9 月份连续第三个月上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/uk-house-prices-climb-for-a-third-month-halifax-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:15:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
