    <item>
      <title>对冲基金在日元 15 年来最大跌幅前买入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/hedge-funds-bought-yen-just-before-ishiba-jobs-jolted-currency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在日本新首相发表鸽派言论和强劲的美国就业报告导致日元遭遇 2009 年底以来最糟糕的一周之前，对冲基金转而看涨日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/hedge-funds-bought-yen-just-before-ishiba-jobs-jolted-currency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 02:45:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据公布后，美国大幅降息的希望消退，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/gold-steady-as-investors-weigh-middle-east-tension-rate-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中东局势持续紧张，且美国就业数据强于预期，削弱了美联储进一步降息半个百分点的预期，但金价仍下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/gold-steady-as-investors-weigh-middle-east-tension-rate-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 23:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注以色列对伊朗袭击的回应，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周油价开盘走低，市场等待观察以色列是否会对上周的导弹袭击对伊朗进行报复，美国总统乔·拜登也不鼓励对伊朗油田进行袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富时指数调整 韩国、印度债券市场备受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/ftse-s-index-revamp-has-korean-indian-bond-markets-on-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国已尽一切努力将其债券纳入主要的富时罗素指数，而印度则避开了公共改革 — — 但后者在全球投资者中的受欢迎程度可能使其在加入相关基准指数方面具有优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/ftse-s-index-revamp-has-korean-indian-bond-markets-on-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
